race.description: Ladbrokes Launceston Cup Packages On Sale Maiden
race.comment: Tricky. On what we've seen, VABUIAGI (14) will be hard to beat. Followed a Hobart trial win with a half-length defeat here on debut over 1000m. She will carry just 52kg with the in-form apprentice aboard, and maps for the race. MEGALITA (6) finished it off well enough here on debut, and the extra metres are sure to suit. Has a wide gate to contend with, but expect him to hit the line hard. The speedy SH'BOURNE RISING (11) debuts and creates plenty of interest with Newitt booked. Missed a nose in her latest trial, and she can enjoy a soft run in transit. VORTISTAR (8) resumes and has switched from a Victorian yard. Went well in the recent trial on the synthetic, and he has a plum gate. The Byrne Burke-Trinder linkage is potent. Has enough ability and looks ready to go.
